CustomField.description: Specifies the Practice that will be associated with Milestones generated for a Product. If provided, will set the Milestone's Override Project Practice. If left blank, the Milestone will be associated with the Project's Practice.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The Practice that will be associated with Milestones generated for the Product, if the Practice should be different from the Project's Practice.
CustomField.label: Practice
